queries.sql: SELECT `tbl_formasi`.`instansi_id`, `tbl_formasi`.`instansi_unor`, `tbl_formasi`.`jabatan_kode`, `formasi_jumlah`, `tbl_jabatan`.`jabatan_nama`, `tbl_unor`.`instansi_unor_nama`, `tbl_pegawai`.`pegawai_nama`, `tbl_pegawai`.`pegawai_nip`, CONCAT(tbl_jabatan.jabatan_nama, tbl_unor.instansi_unor_nama) as jabatan, count(tbl_pegawai.pegawai_nama) as jumlahasn FROM `tbl_formasi` LEFT JOIN `tbl_instansi` ON `tbl_formasi`.`instansi_id` = `tbl_instansi`.`instansi_id` LEFT JOIN `tbl_jabatan` ON `tbl_formasi`.`jabatan_kode` = `tbl_jabatan`.`jabatan_kode` LEFT JOIN `tbl_unor` ON `tbl_unor`.`instansi_unor` = `tbl_formasi`.`instansi_unor` LEFT JOIN `tbl_pegawai` ON `tbl_formasi`.`jabatan_kode` = `tbl_pegawai`.`jabatan_kode` WHERE `tbl_formasi`.`instansi_id` = 'CB' AND `tbl_pegawai`.`instansi_unor` = `tbl_formasi`.`instansi_unor` GROUP BY `jabatan` ORDER BY `tbl_formasi`.`jabatan_kode` asc
